ActFreshwater Fish Marketing Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans of DWIGHT WILLIAMSON of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months, in the place of W. David Olson.
